Put the blue creditcard on the sofa.
Turn around to face the shelf.
Pick up the blue creditcard from the shelf.
Turn around to head back to the sofa.
Put the creditcard on the sofa.

Pick up another credit card from the top shelf.
Go back to the sofa.
Place the second credit card on the sofa.
